version_description: Try On and shop footwear in AR! Wanna Kicks shows you unique technology. This is the first real AR try-on for sneakers.

- Now you can surprise your friends with video, a new way to loop your videos about AR sneakers! Just tap the video camera icon and share your favorite release with friends.
- Also, check out new drops! You've requested Air Max, and 270 model is the best Valentine gift to you all that we could think of.
- Added push notification so that you wouldn't miss coming drops.
- Squashed the bugs, making your experience even better!

- Now you can surprise your friends with video, a new way to loop your videos about AR sneakers! Just tap the video camera icon and share your favorite release with friends.
- Also, check out new drops! You've requested Air Max, and 270 model is the best Valentine gift to you all that we could think of.
- Added push notification so that you wouldn't miss coming drops.
- Squashed the bugs, making your experience even better!
New adidas Ultra Boost 19 in our app! Boost is the most responsive cushioning ever, delivering incredible energy return: the more energy you give, the more you get! Try it today!

Check out new drops!
- Nike M2K Techno release was a real challenge for fashion sneakers world last year. In few months this pair became a real leader in category of sport shoes.
- You've already stopped using plastic bags and began to sort your waste. Next step will be to try on the Allbirds - the best gift you can get from Mother Nature.
- Like running? The Nike Flex Experience RN 7’s - are a good mix of style and comfort. Feel free & easy.
- Meet the Saucony Originals Shadow 5000 Vintage in our app!

New drops are already available! Be the first to check the secret adidas and Nike models.

We've also made shopping easier — just click on the basket to be directed to Amazon or brand website.

New major updates are in progress, soon you'll be able to enjoy new releases with our push notifications!

We're working hard to add more and more drops to the app. Now we're introducing pushes — you'll get one not to miss any of the updates and be the first one to actually Try-On and buy afterwards. Also — a couple of new models added: Aztrek Double X Gigi Hadid and the very exciting YEEZY BOOST 350 V2 TRIPLE WHITE! Yes, we know you've been waiting for them.

Don't forget to search for the new colourways! We won't tell you which ones — better go find yourself!

New sneakers collection in AR!
All cats are grey in the dark. But with the adidas Originals Nite Jogger’s on your feet you can train all night long and feel safe. These sneakers have a lot of retro-reflective details making you more visible! Each model has the inscription “the speed of nite” printed in Morse code on the tongue, insole and sole!

Who said that crystals should be only be found in jewellery? The GUCCI Flashtrek sneakers break the borders between glamour and practicality. Choose them, if you wanna add some vintage to your modern look. And you better insure it because this pair is a real treasure.

What do we say to the God of Cool Sneakers? Today is a day to try on a new pair! Check out the one true quiz "Which Games of Thrones character Are You?". See what color of Ultra boost 4.0 suits you best and find out which family from the Seven Kingdoms it belongs to! Valar Morghulis! Try on with AR!
General Bug Fixes.

The Fila Disruptor 2 is a symbol of the unstoppable in the sneaker world. This archived model from the 90s is making a comeback on big city streets. That’s because its philosophy is very close to the modern generation. Stay strong! Get through the hard times! And wear Fila in AR!

Featured in TechCrunch, Hypebeast, Highsnobiety, Sneaker Freaker, Lifehacker, Geek and more!
General Bug Fixes.
Our app utilizes augmented reality to allow consumers a chance to virtually “try on” sneakers. Give it a try and share your thoughts via sneakers@wanna.by. Your feedback makes us better!
We have improved application stability and fixed crashes.
